	dprr:hasNoteText "Convicted of impudicitia, while serving as Tr. Mil. in the Second Samnite War, by the Tr. Pl. Cominius (Dion. Hal. 16.4; Val. Max. 6.1.11). Dated after 313 by Dion. Hal. Münzer (RE s. v. \"Laetorius\" 11) suggests 292-290, since the story does not appear in Livy." .
